text: Namibia Women's Action for Equality Party was a political party in Namibia. It was formed on 20 July 1994 by Ilenikelao Nhinda Latvio. The party never gained many members and never took part in an election. ==References== Category:Defunct political parties in Namibia Category:Political parties established in 1994 Category:1994 establishments in Namibia Category:Feminist parties in Africa Category:Feminist organisations in Namibia
